sbol:ComponentDefinition.dcterms:title: BBa_K1491031
sbol:ComponentDefinition.dcterms:description: J23115-B0034-T7 RNA Polymerase with Dead ER Intein
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableProvenance: Dead ER intein T7 RNAP is BBa_K1491027, promoter is BBa_J23115, and RBS is BBa_B0034
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableDescription: Dead ER intein T7 RNA polymerase (BBa_K1491027) with constitutive promoter (BBa_J23115) and RBS (BBa_B0034). Includes a 6x His tag.
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableNotes: Constitutive T7 RNAP with Dead ER intein for control
sbol:ComponentDefinition.dc:creator: Danielle Peters

sbol:ComponentDefinition.dcterms:title: BBa_B0034
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableNotes:
Varies from -6 to +1 region from original sequence to accomodate BioBricks suffix.

No secondary structures are formed in the given RBS region. Users should check for secondary structures induced in the RBS by upstream and downstream elements in the +50 to -50 region, as such structures will greatly affect the strength of the RBS. Contact info for this part: Brian Chow
sbol:ComponentDefinition.dc:creator: Vinay S Mahajan, Voichita D. Marinescu, Brian Chow, Alexander D Wissner-Gross and Peter Carr IAP, 2003.

sbol:ComponentDefinition.dcterms:title: BBa_K1491027

sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableProvenance: T7 RNA Polymerase is BBa_K145001 and dead ER intein is BBa_K1491026
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableDescription: T7 RNA polymerase with a non-functional version of the ER intein. Used as a control.
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableNotes: Control for T7 RNA Polyermase with ER intein (BBa_K1491025)
sbol:ComponentDefinition.dc:creator: Danielle Peters

sbol:ComponentDefinition.dcterms:title: BBa_K1491022
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableDescription: Codes for the N-terminus of T7 RNA polymerase (BBa_K145001). This was used to create a T7 polymerase-intein complex.
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableNotes: In order to insert the intein into T7 RNA polymerase, we needed both the N and C terms.
sbol:ComponentDefinition.dc:creator: Danielle Peters
